1
00:00:02,014 --> 00:00:05,000
我们希望能进入神殿并获得尊敬
We wish to sit in the temple and win respect.

2
00:00:05,002 --> 00:00:07,869
我相信以后 你们会记住我的慷慨大方
I trust you will remember my generosity in the days to come.

3
00:00:07,871 --> 00:00:10,505
代表我供万人瞻仰
My likeness in the temple for all to see.

4
00:00:10,507 --> 00:00:14,743
对抗这可憎之物 保卫他的神殿!
Defend his temple against this abomination!

5
00:00:14,745 --> 00:00:18,247
我们点起了一团火 将会把罗马烧成灰烬
We are lighting a fire that will burn Rome to cinders.

6
00:00:18,249 --> 00:00:19,715
去找彼拉多
Go to Pilate.

7
00:00:19,717 --> 00:00:22,784
- 把这座城市从罗马人的屠杀中拯救出来  - 绝不!
- Save this city from a Roman massacre.  - Never!

8
00:00:22,786 --> 00:00:25,287
狂热分子和埃塞俄比亚人结盟了
The zealots have formed an alliance with Ethiopia.

9
00:00:25,289 --> 00:00:29,625
计划发动一场巨大的暴动
They plan to launch a huge uprising against Rome.

10
00:00:29,627 --> 00:00:30,926
走开!
Move aside!

11
00:00:30,928 --> 00:00:32,928
我们被出卖了 快拿!
We are betrayed. Quick!

12
00:00:32,930 --> 00:00:34,863
别管埃塞俄比亚的武器了 我们自己还有
Forget the Ethiopians' weapons. We still have our own.

13
00:00:34,865 --> 00:00:36,098
约亚拿 跟我来
Joanna, come with me.

14
00:00:36,100 --> 00:00:38,967
她会被处死 克劳迪娅
She will be put to death, Claudia.

15
00:00:38,969 --> 00:00:40,269
哥尼流 行刑
Cornelius, begin.

16
00:00:42,173 --> 00:00:44,206
就到此为止吧
This ends here.

