Come on! Pull it!

390
00:28:21,278 --> 00:28:23,279
让开 大祭司
Stand aside, High Priest.

391
00:28:25,983 --> 00:28:28,551
我也是奉命行事
I have my orders.

392
00:28:28,553 --> 00:28:29,886
