Now please stand aside.

393
00:29:42,793 --> 00:29:46,963
那就来吧 百夫长
Do what you have to, centurion.

394
00:29:46,965 --> 00:29:49,933
你可以一拳将我打死
You can kill me with a single blow,

395
00:29:49,935 --> 00:29:52,135
